---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro'
---

<BaseLayout title="About | Glory & Game" description="Learn the mission behind Glory & Game." pathname="/about/">
  <section class="panel">
    <div class="section-heading" style="display:block;">
      <p class="eyebrow">About</p>
      <h1>Why Glory &amp; Game Exists</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        Glory &amp; Game exists for young and older athletes who want more than highlights,
        rankings, and stats. It is a place to discover players whose lives point to Jesus through
        the way they compete, lead, speak, and stay grounded when the spotlight gets bright.
      </p>
      <p class="lead">
        Whether you are trying to grow in your sport, your character, or your faith, we want this
        directory to help you find Christian role models worth looking up to. These stories are
        here to remind the next generation that you can chase excellence, stay humble, and give God
        glory at the same time.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="grid grid-3" style="margin-top: 22px;">
      <div class="flow-card">
        <strong>Celebrate Testimony</strong>
        <span>Highlight athletes whose platform points beyond themselves.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="flow-card">
        <strong>Make Discovery Easy</strong>
        <span>Browse the full directory or search by team, sport, and player.</span>
      </div>
      <div class="flow-card">
        <strong>Dig Into God&apos;s Word</strong>
        <span>Let these stories push you back to Scripture and deeper into a life with Jesus.</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
